Looks good. I like the first. The second one attracts your eyes to that spot where the corner of the phone almost touches the dark area on the left. But maybe this one leaves a little too much space on the right?

White phone on a white background doesn’t make the phone pop out. Swapping white for a color might make the phone pop more. 

I’m not sold on the shadow either, but it anchors the image of the phone. The shadow looks a little weird when it runs into the dark zone.
